  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "When the ork invasion of Rynn's World destroys Arx Tyrannus and leaves the Crimson Fists almost broken, Veteran-Sergeant Sandor Galleas drops behind enemy lines with only a battered Sternguard squad and human survivors from ruined hive-cities. Galleas believes Crimson Fists doctrine is Imperial Fists doctrine perfected, but the wasteland teaches him a different war: ambush, retreat, hunger, civilian courage and losses counted week by week. A successor-chapter survival story about wearing a siege tradition while learning to fight like a guerrilla.",
